And seeing this is my one shot

16:17.208 --> 16:19.959
at impressing you, I'd like
to tip the odds in my favor.

16:20.458 --> 16:21.792
Call in a ringer.

16:22.250 --> 16:24.458
Uh, team's divided,
Henry. There's nobody left.

16:24.458 --> 16:25.375
Sure, there is.

16:25.375 --> 16:27.917
Tailback, slant right.
Z-post on one.

16:27.917 --> 16:30.792
Jack, you run 10 yards out.
Cut to the right flag.

16:30.792 --> 16:32.625
Look over your shoulder.
The ball'll be there.

16:32.625 --> 16:33.583
You ready?

16:33.583 --> 16:34.708
ALL: Break!

16:35.291 --> 16:36.291
