18:04.625 --> 18:06.250
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

18:06.250 --> 18:08.708
How's the first day of classes
goin' there, gorgeous?

18:08.708 --> 18:10.458
Very well, I must say.

18:10.834 --> 18:12.375
I missed you so much.

18:12.708 --> 18:14.417
I missed you, too.

18:14.417 --> 18:15.333
Mmm...

18:15.583 --> 18:17.041
Hey, hey, hey. Get your hands
off my girlfriend.

18:17.041 --> 18:19.083
-[CHUCKLES]
Get your hands off my sister.

18:19.083 --> 18:21.250
-So about tonight...
-What about it?

18:21.750 --> 18:24.333
Well, I was thinkin' since it's
your first Friday back in town,

18:24.333 --> 18:25.959
you and I could
catch a movie

18:25.959 --> 18:27.792
and then stroll down
to our spot.

18:27.792 --> 18:29.375
Oh. Well, I was thinking

18:29.375 --> 18:30.500
we could all grab
dinner tonight,

18:30.500 --> 18:31.750
you know, as a group.

18:31.750 --> 18:33.458
Uh, sorry.
I promised Jen

18:33.458 --> 18:35.959
that I'd go to that, uh,
pep rally.

18:35.959 --> 18:37.250
Well, that could be fun.

18:37.250 --> 18:39.875
Well, in case you forgot,
we're a very non-spirited group,

18:39.875 --> 18:41.792
and pep rallies
are all about spirit.

18:42.583 --> 18:43.917
So what about
you and me?

18:44.542 --> 18:47.333
Well, I mean, there's plenty
of time for us to be alone.

18:47.333 --> 18:50.000
I just kinda want to be
around normal people right now.

18:50.000 --> 18:51.792
You know, it's
been a long time.

18:51.792 --> 18:53.375
[CHUCKLING]
Well, what am I?

18:53.375 --> 18:55.458
Well, she said
normal people.

18:55.458 --> 18:57.125
Ha, ha, ha,
ha, ha.

18:57.625 --> 18:59.458
You know, McPhee,
if I didn't know better,

18:59.792 --> 19:02.417
