to avoid being alone with me.

19:03.708 --> 19:06.333
Uh, no. I mean,
We can be alone after.

19:06.333 --> 19:07.792
Or... or tomorrow.

19:07.792 --> 19:08.875
Ok?

19:09.625 --> 19:10.834
Ok. Bye.

19:13.333 --> 19:15.458
