20:43.208 --> 20:45.083
Ever since Philly,
somebody's been whistling

20:45.083 --> 20:46.667
a very different tune.

20:47.542 --> 20:49.917
It's a Dawson Leery
for the new millennium.

20:49.917 --> 20:52.291
