the words "good" and "time"

20:52.291 --> 20:53.250
in close proximity.

20:53.250 --> 20:56.083
Well, tell me, then,
Dawson 2000,

20:56.417 --> 20:57.875
are you ready
for this good time?

20:58.166 --> 21:00.417
And I don't mean
in a Trojan kind of way.

21:00.708 --> 21:01.583
How do you mean?

21:01.583 --> 21:03.667
Sex isn't a one-way street,
Dawson.

21:04.291 --> 21:06.500
