but no spoon.

21:30.333 --> 21:32.708
Now, it's 100 degrees out,
and you're starving.

21:33.291 --> 21:36.375
Do you lick the ice cream,
or do you bite right in?

21:37.959 --> 21:39.667
-Bite right in.
-Too fast.

21:40.291 --> 21:42.875
See, first you need
to admire the sundae...

21:43.333 --> 21:44.667
Watch the sundae.

21:45.458 --> 21:47.708
And then just before
it's about to drip,

21:47.708 --> 21:49.542
