instead of in your mouth.

22:03.417 --> 22:05.125
But, Dawson, if you
remember one thing,

22:05.125 --> 22:06.375
let it be this...

22:07.417 --> 22:10.083
If you don't get the whipped
cream all over your face...

22:10.458 --> 22:11.959
